<p><tags><tag kind="heading3">### </tag></tags>Markup</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">⌘\</element> for Headlines</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">⌘I</element> for <element kind="emph" startTag="_">emphasize</element></p>
