<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">⌘L</element> for removing any sort of Markup</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">⌘9</element> to show the Markup Bar, in case you can’t remember any of this</p>
